20f2ff32990fc30f6b84ecd912fc472be7abc61","tid":749442,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T16:50:45.000Z","msg":"快D1:1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa39e30b6251a48da7765540171fc99f7668e65f","tid":749442,"uid":79563,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"quote":{"pid":"de4c27d35b028d5c1b478322a517b8c632ccc1b2","tid":749442,"uid":46933,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T16:44:28.000Z","msg":"根本從來都無證實過QE對實體經濟有用<br />\n只係用黎推高資產價格剝奪人民"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T16:55:54.000Z","msg":"QE係避免信貸收緊, 令商業收縮陷入蕭條, 同時令貨幣貶值刺激出口, 賺取外匯<br />\n<br />\nQE同時會令資產價格上升, 但係係金融危機時用QE, 係可以理論上減緩泡沫爆破而令資產價格下跌既速度, 及/或令資產價格較快止跌, 令投資者信心更快穩定<br />\n<br />\n所以QE係有正確既使用方法及時機<br />\n<br />\n但當危機過去, QE就要停, 否則以上各項就會變成副作用危害實體經濟<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n支那國情況係, 信貸已經係瘋狂, money supply已經係超高, 匯率係被操控<br />\n仲QE就係火上加油, 抱薪救火<br />\n<br />\n冥幣匯率無法維持, GDP增長急速放緩, 意味可能快將失控"},{"pid":"7e51ba3bda198309a606806904b9d477f4f2d419","tid":749442,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"220f2ff32990fc30f6b84ecd912fc472be7abc61","tid":749442,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T16:50:45.000Z","msg":"快D1:1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T16:56:12.000Z","msg":"1:1 可能會係樂觀"},{"pid":"f1b60d3995611744fb760a6677cb8505e1bd5031","tid":749442,"uid":90601,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"aa39e30b6251a48da7765540171fc99f7668e65f","tid":749442,"uid":79563,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"quote":{"pid":"de4c27d35b028d5c1b478322a517b8c632ccc1b2","tid":749442,"uid":46933,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T16:44:28.000Z","msg":"根本從來都無證實過QE對實體經濟有用<br />\n只係用黎推高資產價格剝奪人民"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T16:55:54.000Z"